text: Fyodorovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Fyodorovsky Selsoviet of Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 862 as of 2010. There are 13 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yenotayevsky District
title: Fyodorovka, Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
